267
00:20:52,240 --> 00:20:56,360
I have an uneasy feeling about this.

268
00:20:56,360 --> 00:21:01,580
Ever since I parted ways with Brother Yun in Tianqi City over a year ago,

269
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:04,740
I have stopped receiving any news from him.

270
00:21:11,100 --> 00:21:13,920
I, Jinxian, disciple of Grand Eunuch Zhuoqing, have returned.

271
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:17,140
I, Jinwei, disciple of Grand Eunuch Zhuoqing, have returned.

272
00:21:19,320 --> 00:21:22,680
I, Jinyu, disciple of Grand Eunuch Zhuoqing, have returned.

273
00:21:30,140 --> 00:21:32,640
 Zhuoqing suddenly summoned all of his principal disciples,

274
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:35,440
 who have been wandering the martial world, calling them back to the palace.

275
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:38,320
 I'm sure he's up to something.

276
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:02,740
Master.

277
00:22:08,120 --> 00:22:11,600
Jinxian? You've returned?

278
00:22:11,600 --> 00:22:13,700
Forgive me, Master.

279
00:22:22,640 --> 00:22:26,720
I permitted you to wander the martial world for three years.

280
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:29,360
You've done nothing wrong.

281
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:41,360
How was it?

282
00:22:41,360 --> 00:22:44,920
Were there any obstacles on your way back?

283
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:51,260
 I'm Ye Dingzhi, an unnamed swordsman.

284
00:22:56,920 --> 00:22:58,540
No.

285
00:23:15,700 --> 00:23:19,500
Chancellor Chen Ru, long time no see.

286
00:23:19,500 --> 00:23:22,880
Something's off. You're not Mr. Li.

287
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:27,680
Mr. Li told me to come here because his Chun Art has reversed time.

288
00:23:27,680 --> 00:23:31,800
Now, he should look like a young man.

289
00:23:31,800 --> 00:23:33,200
Lower your volume.

290
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:36,840
If not, all of them will hear us.

291
00:23:47,060 --> 00:23:51,700
Eunuch Zhuoqing. Long time no see.

292
00:23:57,740 --> 00:24:01,640
Grand Eunuch, this is a sudden visit. What brings you here?

293
00:24:17,840 --> 00:24:23,820
I’m here to visit the Academy because I have several questions for you, Mr. Chen Ru.

294
00:24:23,820 --> 00:24:27,020
Since this is a visit, why didn’t you enter through the main entrance?

295
00:24:27,020 --> 00:24:29,640
It's because they've sent their men to kill Dongjun.

296
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:33,120
There aren’t many skilled martial artists in Tianqi City who can help them.

297
00:24:33,120 --> 00:24:35,120
He stands the highest chance by visiting our academy.

298
00:24:35,120 --> 00:24:39,280
That's why he's here to visit you.

299
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:41,400
I see.

300
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:45,240
However, he made the wrong move,

301
00:24:45,240 --> 00:24:48,580
as I am here as well.

302
00:24:56,940 --> 00:24:59,400
Show yourself. You all have been tailing me all the way.

303
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:01,860
I picked this spot because there's no one else around.

304
00:25:01,860 --> 00:25:05,700
I hope you all won't disappoint me.

305
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:19,740
Tell me your names so I know who I'm dealing with.

306
00:25:19,740 --> 00:25:21,640
- I'm Xiao Shao. 
 - I'm Jiucheng.

307
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:24,533
- I'm Fenghuang. 
 - I'm Laiyi.

308
00:25:24,533 --> 00:25:26,760
Do you all know who I am, then?

309
00:25:26,760 --> 00:25:28,380
Cut your nonsense!

310
00:25:28,380 --> 00:25:30,840
Brothers, attack!

311
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:34,300
Once, I thought that title was distant from me.

312
00:25:34,300 --> 00:25:38,160
But when I left Tianqi last time, I ascended the stairs with a vat of liquor in hand.

313
00:25:39,660 --> 00:25:43,180
Now that I've returned to Tianqi, I excel in both sword and blade.

314
00:25:44,520 --> 00:25:46,700
I still remember the aspiration I had when I was young.

315
00:25:46,700 --> 00:25:49,540
I was looking forward to announcing this title of mine.

316
00:25:55,880 --> 00:26:00,660
Hello, everyone. I'm Baili Dongjun, the Liquor Deity.

317
00:26:10,560 --> 00:26:14,900
After this battle, the Liquor Deity shall be known throughout the world.

318
00:26:14,900 --> 00:26:16,340
Young Master, please stop!

319
00:26:16,340 --> 00:26:18,680
Fenghuang and I have depended on each other for over 20 years.

320
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:21,900
Young Master, as long as you're willing to spare her,

321
00:26:21,900 --> 00:26:25,400
all four of us are willing to serve as your slaves!

322
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:27,500
I don't need any slaves.

323
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:31,700
Since you all don't want to die, why are you trying to take other people's lives?

324
00:26:31,700 --> 00:26:34,400
Everyone has who they wish to protect.

325
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:38,853
- In the Martial World, we have no choice. 
 - My foot!

326
00:26:38,853 --> 00:26:41,780
All the martial artists I know only act on their own will.

327
00:26:41,780 --> 00:26:43,420
Having no choice

328
00:26:43,420 --> 00:26:46,260
is just an excuse you use to justify your greed.

329
00:26:46,260 --> 00:26:47,620
The Martial World is vast.

330
00:26:47,620 --> 00:26:49,620
I'm sure there's a place for you all.

331
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:52,980
Young Master Baili. What are you...

332
00:26:53,900 --> 00:26:57,140
They only wish to kill me. They won't care about you all.

333
00:26:57,140 --> 00:27:00,200
You should use this chance to escape.

334
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:03,860
Young Master Baili, we will never forget your kindness.

335
00:27:03,860 --> 00:27:05,880
The Martial World is vast.

336
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:09,800
If there's no place for you there, go somewhere else.

337
00:27:09,800 --> 00:27:12,480
I'll remember that.

338
00:27:13,380 --> 00:27:15,600
 That was my first time speaking like a martial arts expert.

339
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:18,400
 - That was quite nerve-wracking.  
 -  Let's go.

340
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:20,400
No, you won't!

341
00:27:38,520 --> 00:27:43,640
Are you the so-called top hit men from the Top Martial Artists Hitmen List?

342
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:45,600
You are useless fools.

343
00:27:45,600 --> 00:27:48,680
I thought I only needed to observe the battle.

344
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:52,780
I never expected that I would have to fight.

345
00:27:54,620 --> 00:27:59,040
Didn't you say you would let us off?

346
00:28:04,460 --> 00:28:09,180
Eunuch, you killed them in your official attire.

347
00:28:09,180 --> 00:28:12,140
Aren't you too arrogant?

348
00:28:12,140 --> 00:28:13,886
So what?

349
00:28:13,886 --> 00:28:18,280
Those who see me will not survive anyway.

350
00:28:23,080 --> 00:28:26,440
Mr. Li and I served in the court for over a decade.

351
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:33,500
Although I don't see him often, he always leaves a deep impression when I do.

352
00:28:33,500 --> 00:28:35,620
You resemble him a lot.

353
00:28:35,620 --> 00:28:38,300
However, you're not him.

354
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:43,300
Why does that touch my heart?

355
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:50,200
Zhuoqing, do you think that Chen Ru and I, an impostor, cannot defeat you two?

356
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:52,240
Why don't we give it a try?

357
00:29:03,780 --> 00:29:06,820
It seems like you're sure that I'm not Li Changsheng.

358
00:29:06,820 --> 00:29:09,700
But I have to give you credit where credit is due.

359
00:29:09,700 --> 00:29:13,400
You're right. I'm not him indeed.

360
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:17,660
It's because I'm wearing a human mask.

361
00:29:27,640 --> 00:29:31,680
Indeed. You're not him.

362
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:33,920
That's right. I'm not him.

363
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:38,020
My name is Nangong Chunshui. I'm a young scholar.

364
00:29:38,020 --> 00:29:39,680
Has it never occurred to you

365
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:44,780
that an impostor of Li Changsheng could be stronger than the real Li Changsheng?

366
00:29:51,020 --> 00:29:56,900
Wait. The Academy is a place for one to study. No fighting allowed.

367
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:02,120
Fine, I'll heed your will.

368
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:05,060
After all, you're the chancellor here.

369
00:30:18,100 --> 00:30:22,040
Those are the top four hit men on the Top Martial Artists Hitmen List?

370
00:30:22,040 --> 00:30:24,780
I spent so much money on you.

371
00:30:24,780 --> 00:30:26,900
What a bunch of useless fools.

372
00:30:26,900 --> 00:30:28,740
Useless!

373
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:40,280
Your Highness.

374
00:30:40,280 --> 00:30:43,080
Your Highness, please be appeased.

375
00:30:43,080 --> 00:30:50,133
If they were good, the Grand Eunuch wouldn't have sent us here.

376
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:22,060
Baili Dongjun, your swordsmanship has exceeded my expectations.

377
00:31:22,060 --> 00:31:24,780
I do hate killing people.

378
00:31:24,780 --> 00:31:26,520
But today,

379
00:31:27,520 --> 00:31:30,280
I want you dead.

380
00:31:30,280 --> 00:31:32,000
What an arrogant statement.

381
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:37,040
Within the palace, I'm one of the top ten swordsmen.

382
00:31:37,040 --> 00:31:38,880
So you're just a small fry.

383
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:41,860
- What did you say? 
 - So what if you're one of the top ten?

384
00:31:41,860 --> 00:31:44,140
Moreover, only the palace is included.

385
00:31:44,140 --> 00:31:46,280
Do you know how vast Tianqi City is? Do you know how vast Beili is?

386
00:31:46,280 --> 00:31:47,960
Do you know how vast the world is?

387
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:51,240
When you face true martial arts experts, they can kill you with a single hand.

388
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:54,480
I only have eyes for the world.

389
00:31:54,480 --> 00:31:58,520
Therefore, to me, you're just a small fry.

390
00:31:59,820 --> 00:32:04,540
If so, what do you think your ranking is in the world?

391
00:32:04,540 --> 00:32:06,500
One of the top 100 swordsmen.

392
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:08,860
You must be kidding me.

393
00:32:08,860 --> 00:32:14,220
Very soon, everyone will know the name Baili Dongjun, the Liquor Deity.

394
00:32:14,220 --> 00:32:18,160
It all depends on whether you can survive this.

